    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/7101927cf721c465a4ee747f2e08eb89.poster.avif?t=1769690798\" width=284 height=34 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/7101927cf721c465a4ee747f2e08eb89.webm?t=1769690798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/7101927cf721c465a4ee747f2e08eb89.mp4?t=1769690798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>用节奏对抗机器人。<br><br>你是Ace，一位正在追捕目标的著名赏金猎手，而你的目标就是疯狂的机器人Frazzer。要想逃脱扭曲诡异的Techno游乐园，你需要掌握射击、飞檐走壁、抓钩飞跃、滑铲与灵活弹跳的窍门，一切尽在节奏之中！准备好你的舞步，在融合Rogue-lite元素的音游射击游戏《ROBOBEAT》中至死方休。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/e84c2c9521be2d1815e4cdf09e79e1cc.poster.avif?t=1769690798\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/e84c2c9521be2d1815e4cdf09e79e1cc.webm?t=1769690798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/e84c2c9521be2d1815e4cdf09e79e1cc.mp4?t=1769690798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >节奏射击</h2>利用自定义音乐功能，享受你的专属节奏吧。很简单，你只要上传并修整你的音轨，或是通过我们的游戏内编辑器来自动生成符合你游戏风格的伴奏。你随时都可以在游戏中更改自定义曲目，毫不费力且不会中断游戏。这项功能支持.wav、.mp3和.ogg文件。只要按照节奏韵律射击就能够造成最大伤害并缩短冷却时间。掌握蓄力射击、伤害系数、穿甲弹等玩法吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/cc3968f1b0d43c188c48a28073db9e59.poster.avif?t=1769690798\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/cc3968f1b0d43c188c48a28073db9e59.webm?t=1769690798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/cc3968f1b0d43c188c48a28073db9e59.mp4?t=1769690798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随音摇曳</h2>酷炫的新武器怎么能少得了同样酷炫的招式。敌人们将不会傻傻地待在原地等你，为了活下来，你将永远不能停下自己的脚步。<br><br>通过飞檐走壁、滑铲、二段跳、兔子跳以及抓钩对抗绚丽缤纷的关卡中的敌人。身随心动，永不止步。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/1cfc83efad71b555f6d38089d6c4de12.poster.avif?t=1769690798\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/1cfc83efad71b555f6d38089d6c4de12.webm?t=1769690798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/1cfc83efad71b555f6d38089d6c4de12.mp4?t=1769690798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >倒带，混音，重放</h2>把《ROBOBEAT》想象成一盘Rogue-lite元素的混音带。<br><br>已迅雷不及掩耳之势穿越随机生成的关卡，装备各式各样的精锐武器并用眼花缭乱的修正选择来扩充自己的军械库。不用拘泥于固定的游玩风格，每一局游戏都将为你带来不一样的体验！<br><br>你能否打破无尽的玄幻，给Frazzer的疯狂行为画上休止符？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/84cbd493363c19f03a77991a30e66961.poster.avif?t=1769690798\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/84cbd493363c19f03a77991a30e66961.webm?t=1769690798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/84cbd493363c19f03a77991a30e66961.mp4?t=1769690798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>用各式各样的枪械与近战武器让敌人们感受音乐的力量；<br></li><li>在眼花缭乱的歌单中挑选出最符合你的游玩风格的音轨。<br></li><li>穿越大宅并解开其中的奥秘，同时在这过程中解锁各类全新歌曲、武器与辅助道具；<br></li><li>用眼睛去感受节奏，歌曲将会改变周遭环境的画风；<br></li><li>通过不计其数的修正选项为自己提供额外加成；<br></li><li>利用行云流水般的动作战胜平台跳跃关卡。</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/998996cd5e41b1e034f4a6c8c6a199d1.poster.avif?t=1769690798\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/998996cd5e41b1e034f4a6c8c6a199d1.webm?t=1769690798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1456760/extras/998996cd5e41b1e034f4a6c8c6a199d1.mp4?t=1769690798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><div class=\"bb_code\">∞ 射击 - 混音 - 重复 ∞\n</div>",
